 Destiny 's Child reunited at the Stellar Gospel Awards in Las Vegas last weekend , it was the first time Beyoncé , Kelly Rowland and Michelle Williams performed together since appearing during the halftime show at Super Bowl in 2013 .
Beyoncé and Kelly joined Michelle 's standing ovation from the 9,000-plus crowd , but they were introduced by their names .
The threesome want to do another ten-year reunion tour and reunion album .